subject: Greetings!
body:
Greetings!
How are you?
I write humbly and hope this meets you well. I thought it vital to remind you.
Since I have not gotten a response to the business proposal I sent you.
I am hoping to get your reply as soon as possible.
I await your correspondence of acknowledgement of receipt.
Have a pleasant day..
Respectfully yours,
Joyce Van Der Est

subject: Re:   Greetings!
body:
Hello Joyce Van Der Est,

I hope this message finds you well. I'm doing fine, thank you for asking. I must apologize, but I don't seem to recall receiving a business proposal from you. Could you please provide me with more details about it? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Have a great day!

Best wishes,
Harry
